      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit broad. Can you dive deeper into the specific role of TNF-alpha in this scaling process? I'm also seeing some weird patterns in the way you're structuring the connection between these papers—it feels less like a standard literature review and more like you're finding some sort of hidden thread. Can you explain the logic behind those connections?",
